{"tid":1900090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙田住戶違反隔離令外出 衛生署回區議員：宜家人手不足 你自己報警啦","createTime":"2020-02-27T04:23:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T05:58:40.000Z","uid":22556,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"64af4059074583c3a6ac2e4e4c285ceb2ed6fa9e","tid":1900090,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:23:38.000Z","msg":"連續兩日有市民違反隔離令！繼前日深水埗黃金電腦商場一名租客擅自開舖營業後，沙田希爾頓中心一名男戶主亦被揭發在家居隔離14天期間多次外出。有區議員接獲居民求助後通知衞生署，惟署方竟稱人手不足，反着議員報警，男戶主昨傍晚疑再度外出，管理處報警求助，警方表示會就事件通知相關部門跟進。<br />\n<br />\n沙田區議員衞慶祥接獲居民求助後，聯絡衞生署反映，要求署方派員上門處理，直至昨早衞生署回覆，但表示人手不足，着他再發現有人違反隔離令，可報警處理。據知，大廈管理處曾翻查大廈出入紀錄，證實涉事男戶主曾多次出入大廈，管理處致電對方交涉不果，惟有加強清潔有關樓層。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10158674431907448/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105259197447%2Fposts%2F10158674431907448%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgXyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=e6cd4d52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10158674431907448/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"df9dfd66e5c58cb09e56b2f6455c3863a7a13f8c","tid":1900090,"uid":9412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:24:11.000Z","msg":"手足？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f36912fc4652e77e1d419a0e86644ead45bc4834","tid":1900090,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:24:15.000Z","msg":"報警仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ee1fec6f3aba23cffd7a7693add5d9c28f71a3","tid":1900090,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:24:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港共"},{"pid":"17a9d6a2a32d4f25bc12f5adbc0d78f14715e66d","tid":1900090,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反彈再反彈<img 